description:
There are a lot of thoughts that have gone through my head at this bar;

Where are all of the hipsters and douche bags? Why, that movie they are playing has a triple headed Russian spy with boobies. Or maybe I am just that drunk. Oh, wait, this is my first bar of the night and I didn't drink before going out this time. That movie they are playing DOES have a triple headed Russian spy with boobies. That last movie I saw here with the sweaty men dancing with snakes and flesh eating Haitians was not at Le Video. Where do they find these films? My sangria tastes good. My old fashioned tastes good and is nice and strong. My _______ tastes good. The bathroom has toilet paper....and no line. I want a cigarette. I just smoked one out back next to the no smoking sign and no one yelled at me. What is lurking in that back closet. Why is it so easy to get served here? If we keep holding their moodalicious candles up to our heads acting emo will our hair catch on fire? What would Christopher K look like bald? Happy Birthday to me, why am I too tired to finish my drink, I must be slipping. Nice mellow vibe without any pretension. Is this place really in the Mission? Great song! Yay. 

I am sure there are other things I have thought, as this bar is a great place to come talk and drink and think random thoughts. I think. I drink. Therefore I am (drunk, that is). Stay out of this bar. I like it.
